** Primary Colors
Red Green and Blue
** Secondary Colors
- Green
- Orange
- Purple
** By Temperature
*** Cool Colors
**** Cerulean Blue
**** Ultramarine Blue -deep blue color pigment originally made by grinding lapis lazuli into a powder
**** Pthalo Blue - brighter blue
*** Warm Colors
**** Burnt Sienna - heated raw sienna yellowish brown
**** Yellow ochre - earth pigment, ferric oxide
**** Crimson Red - a deep rich shade of red with hints of prurple and blue.
